title: Evanston, Northwestern Announce Details of $1M Donation (Northwestern University)
text: ( Source : Northwestern University ) EVANSTON, Ill. --- Evanston Mayor Elizabeth Tisdahl and Northwestern University President Morton Schapiro announced today (Oct. 9) the allocation of the first $1 million donation from Northwestern
